  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK177">
<l>vēṇṭaṟka veḵkiyā mākkam viṉaivayiṉ</l>
<l>māṇṭaṟ karitām payaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Desire not the gain of covetousness. In the enjoyment of its fruits there is no glory.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
